{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"The moment I say \"school,\""},{"time":3000,"text":"so many memories come back to me."},{"time":7000,"text":"It's like after every exam,\nwhen I walk out,"},{"time":10000,"text":"the teacher would say, \"Hey, come."},{"time":12000,"text":"How did you do?\""},{"time":14000,"text":"I would say with a great smile,\n\"I will definitely pass.\""},{"time":16000,"text":"And I didn't understand why,"},{"time":18000,"text":"in one hand they say, \"Speak the truth,\""},{"time":20000,"text":"in the other hand, when you say\nthe truth, they hated you."},{"time":22786,"text":"So it went on like that,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and I didn't know where\nelse to find myself."},{"time":27000,"text":"So I remember those nights"},{"time":29000,"text":"I used to go to sleep"},{"time":31000,"text":"with asking help from [the] Unknown"},{"time":34000,"text":"because, for some reason,"},{"time":36000,"text":"I couldn't believe\nwhat my father and mother"},{"time":38120,"text":"hanged in the Puja room as a god,"},{"time":41000,"text":"because my friend's family"},{"time":43000,"text":"had something else as a god."},{"time":45000,"text":"So I thought, \"I guess\nI'll pray to [the] Unknown"},{"time":47358,"text":"and ask help,\""},{"time":50000,"text":"and started getting help from everywhere,"},{"time":52000,"text":"each and every corner\nof my life at that time."},{"time":56000,"text":"My brothers started giving me\na few tips about drawing and painting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59263,"text":"Then, when I was in eighth standard"},{"time":62000,"text":"around 13 years old,"},{"time":65000,"text":"I started working in a part-time job"},{"time":67000,"text":"in one of the signboard\nartists called Putu."},{"time":72952,"text":"And then school also\nstarted supporting me."},{"time":75000,"text":"\"Oh, he's bad at studies,"},{"time":77000,"text":"but let him send\nto the drawing competitions.\""},{"time":80000,"text":"So it was good to survive\nwith that little tool"},{"time":83000,"text":"that I found to find\nmy own place in school."},{"time":87000,"text":"And one of those competitions,"},{"time":89000,"text":"I just won a small,\nlittle transistor Philips radio."},{"time":92000,"text":"And I didn't have the patience to wait"},{"time":94000,"text":"until I reached home."},{"time":96000,"text":"So I just switched\non in the train, loudly."},{"time":98072,"text":"If you travel in Indian trains,"},{"time":100000,"text":"you can see people listening to radio"},{"time":102000,"text":"and, you know, even from their mobiles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"So at that time -- and I was 13 --"},{"time":106000,"text":"and I was listening to just radio,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and someone happened to sit next to me,"},{"time":111000,"text":"like these three people are sitting here."},{"time":113000,"text":"You know, like just adjacent to me."},{"time":115000,"text":"He just started asking, \"Where did\nyou buy the radio? How much is it?\""},{"time":118358,"text":"I said, \"It's a prize\nfrom [an] art competition.\""},{"time":121000,"text":"And he said, \"Oh, I teach\nat a college of arts."},{"time":124000,"text":"I think"},{"time":126000,"text":"you should study in a school of art."},{"time":128000,"text":"You just quit school and come there.\""},{"time":130000,"text":"So, why I'm telling you this,"},{"time":132000,"text":"you know, maybe, you know,"},{"time":134000,"text":"whoever is sitting next to you can\nchange your whole life -- it's possible."},{"time":137596,"text":"It is that we need we need\nto be open and fine-tuned."},{"time":141000,"text":"So that's what made me enter"},{"time":144000,"text":"[the] college of arts after three attempts"},{"time":147000,"text":"and just continue to inquire"},{"time":150000,"text":"what I really want to do\nwith art work, or art"},{"time":153000,"text":"and finally I'm here in front of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"When I look back, you know,"},{"time":157000,"text":"on what happened between that time"},{"time":159000,"text":"and now here --"},{"time":162000,"text":"the last 10/15 years --"},{"time":164000,"text":"I can see that most of the works"},{"time":166000,"text":"revolve around three subjects,"},{"time":169000,"text":"but it was not intentional."},{"time":171000,"text":"And I just start out with a trace\nbecause I was thinking,"},{"time":173000,"text":"\"What really makes us?\" -- you know,"},{"time":175000,"text":"it's actually [the] past,\nwhat makes a person."},{"time":179000,"text":"So I was thinking,"},{"time":181000,"text":"but when you look at the past,"},{"time":183000,"text":"the way to understand the past"},{"time":185000,"text":"is only by the traces available,"},{"time":187000,"text":"because we cannot go back [to] the past."},{"time":189000,"text":"It can be ruins, or it can be music,"},{"time":191000,"text":"or it can be painting or drawing\nor writing, whatever it is."},{"time":194000,"text":"But it is just a kind\nof trace of that time."},{"time":199000,"text":"And that fascinated me,"},{"time":201000,"text":"to explore that territory."},{"time":205000,"text":"So I was working on the line,"},{"time":208000,"text":"but instead of working about traces,"},{"time":212000,"text":"I started capturing traces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"So here are some of the works\nI would like to show you."},{"time":218000,"text":"So this is called \"Self In Progress.\""},{"time":221000,"text":"It's just a trace of being in this body."},{"time":224000,"text":"So here, what happened then,"},{"time":226000,"text":"you know -- what I really enjoyed the most"},{"time":228000,"text":"is that this sculpture"},{"time":230000,"text":"is nothing but a trace of myself."},{"time":234000,"text":"It's almost like a 3D photograph."},{"time":236000,"text":"So there is an element of performance,"},{"time":238000,"text":"and there is an element of sculpture,"},{"time":240000,"text":"and there is an element of feeling\none's self, so close to one's self."},{"time":243358,"text":"So it's almost like fossils\nfor the future."},{"time":246000,"text":"And then moved slowly"},{"time":248000,"text":"to explore the other possibilities\nof capturing traces."},{"time":254000,"text":"So this is what I was talking\nabout, while molding,"},{"time":257000,"text":"it's such a great experience,"},{"time":259000,"text":"because we have freedom of like walking,"},{"time":261000,"text":"or moving my hand or,\nmoving around in the space,"},{"time":264000,"text":"but the moment this becomes solid,"},{"time":267000,"text":"when you cannot move even an inch,"},{"time":270000,"text":"because this is plaster of Paris, so\nthe moment you pour it it's like liquid;"},{"time":273691,"text":"but after 20 minutes,\nit's almost like a hard stone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"So this is capturing\nthe trace of a thumbprint"},{"time":281000,"text":"because, knowingly or unknowingly,"},{"time":283000,"text":"whatever we do, you know,\nwe leave our traces here."},{"time":286000,"text":"So I just thought, \"I'm going to capture"},{"time":289000,"text":"thumbprint, footprint,"},{"time":291000,"text":"or whatever traces we leave as humans.\""},{"time":294000,"text":"This is the trace of fire,"},{"time":297000,"text":"this is the trace of sun."},{"time":300000,"text":"Because when I was capturing\ntraces, you know,"},{"time":302215,"text":"this thought comes to me always:"},{"time":305000,"text":"is it, only when the object touches\nthe thing and it leaves the trace,"},{"time":308000,"text":"or is there other ways to capture it?\""},{"time":310000,"text":"So this work is nothing but like --"},{"time":312000,"text":"because of the focal length of the lens,"},{"time":314000,"text":"it just shows what is on the other side."},{"time":318000,"text":"So I just put the paper\non the focal length,"},{"time":320120,"text":"which was an etching print,"},{"time":322000,"text":"then I got the portrait\nof [the] sun from sunlight."},{"time":326000,"text":"This is called \"Dawn to Dawn.\""},{"time":328000,"text":"What I did here, I just put\nlike 10 feet [of] paper"},{"time":331000,"text":"then put a coconut rope,"},{"time":333000,"text":"and just burnt it."},{"time":335000,"text":"So it took about 24\nhours to get this line."},{"time":337048,"text":"So wherever the fire is eating the paper,"},{"time":339048,"text":"that's what becomes the work --"},{"time":341000,"text":"detail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Even though we have traces"},{"time":349000,"text":"when we try to understand them,"},{"time":353000,"text":"the perception and context"},{"time":355000,"text":"play a major role to understand it."},{"time":357000,"text":"So do we really understand what it is,"},{"time":360000,"text":"or are we trying to get"},{"time":362000,"text":"what we think it is?"},{"time":364000,"text":"Then move towards questioning\nthe perception"},{"time":366120,"text":"because, even though there are traces,"},{"time":368000,"text":"when you try to understand them,\nyou know you play a major role."},{"time":371072,"text":"So like let's say even a simple act."},{"time":373000,"text":"How many of you saw\na cow crossing in India"},{"time":376000,"text":"while you were coming\nfrom Bangalore to Mysore?"},{"time":378263,"text":"Can you just raise the hand?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"If you just ask an opinion"},{"time":383000,"text":"of how, everyone can interpret it."},{"time":386000,"text":"Like, let's say, if a schoolteacher says,"},{"time":388000,"text":"she'll simply say, \"To\nget to the other side.\""},{"time":390215,"text":"Why the cow was crossing\nthe road, you know."},{"time":393000,"text":"The answer can be so\ndifferent if Potter said it."},{"time":396000,"text":"He would say, \"For the greater good.\""},{"time":399000,"text":"Martin Luther King would say,"},{"time":401000,"text":"\"I imagine a world where\nall cows will be free"},{"time":404000,"text":"to cross the road,"},{"time":406000,"text":"without having their motives\ncalled into question.\""},{"time":409000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":411000,"text":"Imagine Moses comes now, and he sees"},{"time":413000,"text":"the same cow walking around the street."},{"time":415000,"text":"He would definitely say,"},{"time":417000,"text":"\"God came down from heaven,"},{"time":420000,"text":"and he said unto the cow,"},{"time":423000,"text":"'Thou shalt cross the road.'"},{"time":426000,"text":"And cow crossed the road,"},{"time":428000,"text":"and there was much\nrejoicing as a holy cow.\""},{"time":431000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":433000,"text":"Freud would say,"},{"time":435000,"text":"\"The fact that you're at all concerned"},{"time":437000,"text":"reveals your underlying\nsexual insecurity.\""},{"time":440000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":442000,"text":"If we ask Einstein,"},{"time":444000,"text":"he would say, \"Whether\nthe cow crossed the road,"},{"time":447000,"text":"or the road moved underneath the cow,"},{"time":449000,"text":"depends on your frame of reference.\""},{"time":451000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":453000,"text":"Or Buddha --"},{"time":455000,"text":"if he saw the same cow, he would say,"},{"time":457000,"text":"\"Asking this question denies\nyour own nature [as a] cow.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":460000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"So, what we see"},{"time":466000,"text":"is just what we think often,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and most of the time,\nwe don't see what it is."},{"time":472000,"text":"It just all depends on one's perception."},{"time":475000,"text":"And context, what is really context?"},{"time":478000,"text":"You know, I could just show you\nthis little piece of paper."},{"time":481000,"text":"Because I always think meaning\ndoesn't really exist."},{"time":486000,"text":"The meaning of what we create\nin this world doesn't exist."},{"time":488786,"text":"It's just created by the mind."},{"time":491000,"text":"If you look at this piece of paper,"},{"time":494000,"text":"this is the breadth"},{"time":496000,"text":"and this is called length."},{"time":498000,"text":"This is how we've been taught in school."},{"time":502000,"text":"But if you tear it in the middle --"},{"time":505000,"text":"now, I didn't touch this breadth,"},{"time":507000,"text":"but still, the meaning of this changes."},{"time":509000,"text":"So what we conceive as a meaning"},{"time":511000,"text":"is always not there;"},{"time":513000,"text":"it's on the other side,"},{"time":515000,"text":"even when we say dark, light,"},{"time":517000,"text":"good, bad, tall, short --"},{"time":519000,"text":"all meaning it doesn't exist in reality."},{"time":522000,"text":"It's just that being a human,"},{"time":524000,"text":"the way we train to perceive the reality"},{"time":527000,"text":"creates this meaning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"So this work from this period"},{"time":531000,"text":"is mostly like --"},{"time":533000,"text":"you know, this is a work\ncalled \"Light Makes Dark.\""},{"time":535453,"text":"It's just captured through from the lamp."},{"time":538000,"text":"So the lamp is not just giving\na light, it's also giving a darkness."},{"time":541263,"text":"So this is a work of art,\nwhich is just trying to explore that."},{"time":545000,"text":"This is called \"Limit Out.\""},{"time":547000,"text":"This shows how limited our eye\nor hearing sense or touch --"},{"time":550000,"text":"do we really see?"},{"time":552000,"text":"This is an exact negative."},{"time":554000,"text":"It's about six inches deep in the wall,"},{"time":556000,"text":"but it just appears\nlike it's coming out of the wall."},{"time":562000,"text":"You know the wall is almost like --"},{"time":564000,"text":"this is the first skin,\nand this is the second,"},{"time":566239,"text":"and there's a third,\nand each creates a meaning."},{"time":568549,"text":"And we're just pulling\nthe wall off the gallery."},{"time":571000,"text":"Again, \"Inward Out.\""},{"time":573000,"text":"It's a full-figure cast from myself."},{"time":575000,"text":"It's about eight inches deep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"When I was doing that, I always wondered\nsince I've worked with creators --"},{"time":584000,"text":"and now you know, I've moved\nto questioning the perception --"},{"time":587000,"text":"whenever I see the bird flying in the sky,"},{"time":590000,"text":"it just makes me feel like:"},{"time":593000,"text":"is there anything behind,\nare there any traces up there,"},{"time":596000,"text":"which as a human, we don't see them?"},{"time":599000,"text":"Is there any way to capture the thought"},{"time":602000,"text":"into visual art?"},{"time":605000,"text":"I couldn't find it."},{"time":608000,"text":"But a solution arrived"},{"time":611000,"text":"after being quiet and not working\nfor about six, seven months,"},{"time":614000,"text":"in the restroom,"},{"time":616000,"text":"when I was changing the air freshener"},{"time":619000,"text":"that goes from solid substance to vapor."},{"time":621000,"text":"It's called Odonil."},{"time":623000,"text":"This is the work I made\nout of that material."},{"time":627000,"text":"The process to get to make\nthe sculpture was interesting,"},{"time":629691,"text":"because I wrote to Balsara,"},{"time":631000,"text":"who produces that air\nfreshener called Odonil,"},{"time":633000,"text":"saying, \"Dear Sir, I am an artist.\nThis is my catalogue."},{"time":635000,"text":"Will you help me to make this sculpture?\""},{"time":637000,"text":"They never wrote back to me."},{"time":639000,"text":"Then I thought, \"I will go\nto the Small Scale Industries"},{"time":642000,"text":"Facilitating Unit and ask help.\""},{"time":644000,"text":"So I told them, \"I'd like to start\nan air freshener company.\""},{"time":648000,"text":"They said, \"Of course."},{"time":650000,"text":"This is the fee for the project report,"},{"time":652000,"text":"and we will give you\nall the details,\" and they gave."},{"time":654548,"text":"Finally, I went back to them and said,"},{"time":657000,"text":"\"It's not for starting the company,\nit's just to make my own work."},{"time":660167,"text":"Please come for the show.\""},{"time":662000,"text":"And they did."},{"time":664000,"text":"And this work is in the Devi\nArt Foundation in Delhi."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"In India, nobody really\ntalks about works of art;"},{"time":670000,"text":"they always talk\nabout the appreciation of art."},{"time":673000,"text":"You buy this for 3,000 rupees,"},{"time":675000,"text":"it'll become 30,000 in two months."},{"time":677000,"text":"This is the craft that was going on,"},{"time":679000,"text":"but there are a few collectors"},{"time":681000,"text":"who also collect art which can depreciate."},{"time":683000,"text":"And this was collected by Anupam --"},{"time":685000,"text":"which is like, finally in the end,\nhe will not have anything,"},{"time":687929,"text":"because it will evaporate."},{"time":691000,"text":"So this is after a few weeks,"},{"time":694000,"text":"this is after a few months."},{"time":696000,"text":"It's just all about questioning\nthe preconceptions."},{"time":699000,"text":"So if someone says, \"Oh,\nI see the portrait,\""},{"time":702000,"text":"it may not be the portrait\nafter a few months."},{"time":704215,"text":"And if they say it's solid,"},{"time":706000,"text":"it will not be solid, it will evaporate."},{"time":709000,"text":"And if they say they don't get it,"},{"time":711000,"text":"that's also not true,"},{"time":713000,"text":"because it's in the air."},{"time":715000,"text":"It's in the same gallery\nor in the same museum."},{"time":717263,"text":"So they inhaled it,"},{"time":719000,"text":"but they are not aware of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"While I was doing that work,"},{"time":724000,"text":"my mom and my dad,"},{"time":726000,"text":"they were looking at it and they said,"},{"time":728000,"text":"\"Why do you deal with negative\nsubjects all the time?\""},{"time":731000,"text":"And I was like, \"What do you mean?\""},{"time":733000,"text":"\"Light makes dark and now\nevaporating self."},{"time":736000,"text":"Don't you think it remained\nsomething about death,\" they said."},{"time":739000,"text":"\"Of course not. For me,\" I'm thinking,"},{"time":741000,"text":"\"this is tucked in some small solid,"},{"time":743000,"text":"but the moment it evaporates,"},{"time":745000,"text":"it's merged with the whole.\""},{"time":747000,"text":"But she said, \"No. Still, I don't like it."},{"time":749000,"text":"Can you make something from nothing"},{"time":751000,"text":"as a sculptor?\""},{"time":753000,"text":"I said, \"No, mom. It can't be."},{"time":755000,"text":"Because we can create"},{"time":758000,"text":"a sculpture"},{"time":760000,"text":"by gathering dust together,"},{"time":762000,"text":"or we can break the sculpture\nand get the dust,"},{"time":765000,"text":"but there is nowhere that we can\nbring dust into the universe.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":768000,"text":"So, I did this work for her."},{"time":771000,"text":"It's called \"Emerging Angel.\""},{"time":773000,"text":"This is the first day --"},{"time":775000,"text":"it just gives the appearance"},{"time":777000,"text":"that one is becoming the other."},{"time":779000,"text":"So, the same sculpture"},{"time":781000,"text":"after a few days."},{"time":785000,"text":"This is after 15/20 days."},{"time":788000,"text":"Through that small little slit"},{"time":790000,"text":"between the glass box and the wood,"},{"time":792000,"text":"the air goes underneath the sculpture\nand creates the other one."},{"time":795072,"text":"This gave me a greater faith."},{"time":797000,"text":"That evaporating sculpture\ngave me a greater faith"},{"time":800000,"text":"that maybe there\nis many more possibilities"},{"time":802072,"text":"to capture [the] invisible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804000,"text":"So what you see now"},{"time":806000,"text":"is called \"Shadow Foreshadow.\""},{"time":809000,"text":"And what I'd like to tell you"},{"time":811000,"text":"is we don't see shadow,\nand we don't see light too;"},{"time":814000,"text":"we see the source of the light."},{"time":816000,"text":"We see where it's bouncing,\nbut we don't see [them] as they exist."},{"time":819167,"text":"You know, that's why the night\nsky, we see the sky as dark,"},{"time":822000,"text":"but it's filled with light all the time."},{"time":824000,"text":"When it's bounced on the moon, we see it."},{"time":826000,"text":"The same thing in the darkroom."},{"time":828000,"text":"The little dust particle\nwill again, reflect the light,"},{"time":831000,"text":"and we realize the existence of light."},{"time":833000,"text":"So we don't see dark, we don't see light,"},{"time":836000,"text":"we don't see gravity,\nwe don't see electricity."},{"time":839000,"text":"So, I just started doing this work"},{"time":842000,"text":"to inquire further"},{"time":845000,"text":"about how to sculpt"},{"time":847000,"text":"the space between this object and there."},{"time":850000,"text":"Because, as a visual artist, if I'm\nseeing this and I'm seeing that --"},{"time":853358,"text":"but how to sculpt this, you know?"},{"time":856000,"text":"If we sculpt this, this\nhas two reference points."},{"time":859000,"text":"The skin of this is also\nrepresenting this."},{"time":862000,"text":"And skin at the other end\nalso represents the floor."},{"time":865000,"text":"I did this as an experiment"},{"time":868000,"text":"of casting the shadow."},{"time":870000,"text":"So this is a corrugated\nbox and its shadow."},{"time":873000,"text":"Then the second one --"},{"time":875000,"text":"the moment you bring any invisible\ninto the visible world"},{"time":878000,"text":"it will have all the characteristics\nof the visible existence."},{"time":881000,"text":"So that produced a shadow."},{"time":883000,"text":"Then I thought, okay, let me sculpt that."},{"time":885000,"text":"Then, again, that becomes an object."},{"time":887000,"text":"Again, throwing light, then the third one."},{"time":890000,"text":"So what you see is nothing but shadow"},{"time":892000,"text":"of a shadow of a shadow."},{"time":894000,"text":"And then again, at that point,\nthere is no shadow."},{"time":897000,"text":"I thought, \"Oh, good. Work is finished.\""},{"time":901000,"text":"You can see the detail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907000,"text":"This is called \"Gravity.\""},{"time":914000,"text":"It's called \"Breath.\" It's just\ntwo holes on the gallery wall."},{"time":917000,"text":"It's a false wall, which contains"},{"time":919000,"text":"like 110 cubic feet."},{"time":921000,"text":"So that hole actually"},{"time":923000,"text":"makes the air come out and go in."},{"time":926000,"text":"So where it's happening, we can see,"},{"time":928000,"text":"but what is happening\nwill remain invisible only."},{"time":930334,"text":"This is from the show called\n\"Invisible,\" at Talwar Gallery."},{"time":933334,"text":"This is called \"Kaayam.\""},{"time":935000,"text":"Detail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"And what I'd like to tell you,"},{"time":943000,"text":"our senses are so limited --"},{"time":945000,"text":"we cannot hear everything,\nwe cannot see everything."},{"time":947000,"text":"We don't feel, \"I am touching the air,\""},{"time":949000,"text":"but if the breeze is a little more\nfaster, then I can feel it."},{"time":953000,"text":"So all of our construction of reality"},{"time":956000,"text":"is through these limited senses."},{"time":958000,"text":"So my request was like,"},{"time":960000,"text":"is there any way to use all this"},{"time":962000,"text":"as just a symbol or a sign?"},{"time":966000,"text":"And to really get to the point,"},{"time":968000,"text":"we should move beyond, you know,"},{"time":970000,"text":"go to the other side\nof the wall, like illogic,"},{"time":972263,"text":"like are invisible."},{"time":974000,"text":"Because when we see someone\nwalks, we see the footprint."},{"time":976000,"text":"But if we're just cutting that footprint\nfrom the whole thing and trying to analyze it,"},{"time":979000,"text":"you will miss the point"},{"time":981000,"text":"because the actual journey happens\nbetween those footprints,"},{"time":984000,"text":"and the footprints are nothing\nbut passing time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":986310,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":988000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}